In light of my actions, I have already taken steps to demonstrate my commitment to making amends. I have voluntarily enrolled in a defensive driving course to enhance my knowledge and skills, ensuring that such offenses will not recur in the future. Additionally, I have sought therapy and implemented strategies to better manage my ADHD, as mentioned in the input story, showing my dedication to personal growth and self-improvement.

Lastly, I want to express the genuine remorse I feel for the danger I created and the inconveniences I caused. I understand the gravity of my actions and the potential consequences they could have had. I am committed to learning from this experience and becoming a law-abiding citizen who contributes positively to society.

